      "answer": "[2] [3]\n\nThe evidence indicates that the approval for whether new article attributes are useful rather than unmanaged data requires validation and is currently an open question. Specifically, it mentions \"Who owns article attributes by type?\" as a topic requiring validation due to the risk of attributes becoming unmanaged without clear ownership.\n\nTherefore, based on the evidence, this decision needs to be validated and confirmed by business owners across support, assets, finance or other relevant teams."
